high_descs: Turn right and walk to the head of lettuce on the white table and turn right to face it once you get to it.
Pick up the knife that's in front of you near the potato to the right of the lettuce..
Cut the potato into slices with your knife.
Put the knife on the table to the left of the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the microwave turning right to face it once you get there.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left.
Put the slice of potato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward and turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Cut the potato on the table into slices.
Place the knife on the white table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn left to face the trash can.
Place the potato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To hear a potato slice and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, go across the room and turn right towards the white table.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the table.
Cut the potato on the table.
Put the knife on the table beside the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and head to the microwave in the corner.
Put the slice of potato on the plate in the microwave, cook the potato and take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn right, go across the room and turn left to face the black trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the trash can.
